      <h2>Reading Experience</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Dark / light mode</strong> &mdash; toggle in the masthead; respects system preference on first visit; preference saved locally</li>
        <li><strong>Reading progress bar</strong> &mdash; fixed at the top of article pages; stops at the end of the body text</li>
        <li><strong>Focus mode</strong> &mdash; hides the site masthead for distraction-free reading</li>
        <li><strong>Reading settings</strong> &mdash; font size slider and typeface choice (Serif / Sans / OpenDyslexic)</li>
        <li><strong>Read aloud</strong> &mdash; text-to-speech with play/pause/stop, speed presets, and voice selector</li>
        <li><strong>Table of contents</strong> &mdash; auto-generated from headings on article pages with scroll-spy highlighting</li>
        <li><strong>Heading anchor links</strong> &mdash; link icon on hover for deep-linking to any section</li>
        <li><strong>Back to top button</strong> &mdash; appears after scrolling down on article pages</li>
        <li><strong>Reading time</strong> &mdash; calculated from word count; shown on every article card and article page</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Article Tools</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Save to reading list</strong> &mdash; bookmark any article in the browser; no account required; accessible at <a href="/reading-list/">/reading-list/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Share</strong> &mdash; share panel with social media links, copy link, and email</li>
        <li><strong>Download</strong> &mdash; export article as plain text (.txt) or Markdown (.md)</li>
        <li><strong>Print</strong> &mdash; print-optimised layout; works for PDF saving</li>
        <li><strong>Cite</strong> &mdash; citation modal with APA 7th, MLA 9th, and Chicago 17th formats</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Content &amp; Editorial</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Eight sections</strong> &mdash; <a href="/travel/">Travel</a>, <a href="/poetry/">Poetry</a>, <a href="/entertainment/">Entertainment</a>, <a href="/fashion/">Fashion</a>, <a href="/art/">Art</a>, <a href="/music/">Music</a>, <a href="/dance/">Dance</a>, and <a href="/letters/">Letters</a></li>
        <li><strong>Editions</strong> &mdash; collected editions at <a href="/editions/">/editions/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Corrections</strong> &mdash; transparent corrections log at <a href="/corrections/">/corrections/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Letters to the editor</strong> &mdash; reader correspondence at <a href="/letters/">/letters/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Newsletter</strong> &mdash; email subscription via Buttondown at <a href="/newsletter/">/newsletter/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Submit</strong> &mdash; submit a piece for publication at <a href="/submit/">/submit/</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Navigation &amp; Discovery</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Full-site search</strong> via Pagefind &mdash; built at deploy time, no backend</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile nav drawer</strong> &mdash; full site navigation in a slide-out drawer</li>
        <li><strong>Surprise Me</strong> &mdash; button that redirects to a random article</li>
        <li><strong>Related articles</strong> &mdash; shown at the bottom of every article</li>
        <li><strong>Tags / topics index</strong> at <a href="/topics/">/topics/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Archives</strong> at <a href="/archives/">/archives/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Style guide</strong> &mdash; brand and design reference at <a href="/style-guide/">/style-guide/</a></li>
        <li><strong>Masthead</strong> &mdash; editorial information at <a href="/masthead/">/masthead/</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Technical</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Progressive Web App</strong> &mdash; web manifest, service worker, offline fallback</li>
        <li><strong>XML sitemap</strong> at <a href="/sitemap.xml">/sitemap.xml</a></li>
        <li><strong>RSS feed</strong> at <a href="/feed.xml">/feed.xml</a></li>
        <li><strong>JSON-LD structured data</strong> on article pages</li>
        <li><strong>Print CSS</strong> &mdash; clean article output for printing</li>
        <li><strong>Bunny Fonts</strong> &mdash; privacy-friendly font loading</li>
        <li><strong>Hosted on Cloudflare Pages</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Privacy &amp; Accessibility</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>No first-party cookies</strong> &mdash; all preferences stored locally in your browser</li>
        <li><strong>No advertising or tracking pixels</strong></li>
        <li><strong>Skip-to-main link</strong> &mdash; for keyboard and screen reader navigation</li>
        <li><strong>OpenDyslexic font</strong> &mdash; available via the reading settings panel</li>
        <li><strong>ARIA labels</strong> on all interactive elements</li>
        <li><strong>Privacy policy</strong> at <a href="/privacy/">/privacy/</a></li>
      </ul>

